divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside, on my balcony of my house in Orfu, Hungary. I was playing around with my digital camera and took a picture of the moon. At the time I did not notice anything in the sky. Just the other day I was looking over my pictures to see which ones I should delete to make room on my hard drive. I came to this picture, I zoomed in and noticed the objects in the air. I'm not sure what it is, but I thought I would send it to your office. You have more experience with these types of things. I will send the original picture I took.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Orfű
